description:
In this video, I use the p5.js library to create a web-based countdown timer. I discuss the native JavaScript method setInterval() as well as p5's millis(). 

💻Challenge: https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/066-timer.html

Links discussed in this video:
🔗millis() reference: https://p5js.org/reference/#/p5/millis
🔗getURLParams() reference: https://p5js.org/reference/#/p5/getURLParams
